or:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$fichierDump<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">,<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$entete<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n    <span style=\"color:#990000;\">fwrite<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$fichierDump<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">,<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$creations<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n    <span style=\"color:#990000;\">fwrite<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$fichierDump<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">,<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$insertions<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n    <span style=\"color:#990000;\">fclose<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$fichierDump<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#125;<\/span><\/pre><\/td><\/tr><\/table><\/div>","wfw:commentRss":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/sauvegarder-votre-base-de-donnees-mysql-dans-un-fichier-sql-dumpmysql\/feed","slash:comments":"0","y:published":{"hour":"16","timezone":"UTC","second":"49","month":"8","month_name":"August","minute":"41","utime":"1312216909","day":"1","day_ordinal_suffix":"st","day_of_week":"1","day_name":"Monday","year":"2011"},"y:id":{"permalink":"false","value":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/?p=22"},"y:title":"Sauvegarder votre base de donn\u00e9es MySQL dans un fichier .sql: dumpMySQL()","guid":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/sauvegarder-votre-base-de-donnees-mysql-dans-un-fichier-sql-dumpmysql"},{"title":"Fonction PHP pour cr\u00e9er un \u2018slug\u2019, un identifiant URL-friendly","link":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/fonction-php-pour-creer-un-slug-un-identifiant-url-friendly","comments":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/fonction-php-pour-creer-un-slug-un-identifiant-url-friendly#comments","pubDate":"Sun, 31 Jul 2011 16:00:59 +0000","dc:creator":"julien","category":["Webdev","fonctions","php","seo","slug","snippet","url-friendly"],"description":"Je parlais il n&#8217;y a pas longtemps des slugs dans WordPress et comment coder une fonction get_the_slug(). Il s&#8217;agit d&#8217;un identifiant URL-firiendly. L&#8217;id\u00e9e est de le passer en argument dans l&#8217;adresse et d&#8217;\u00e9crire ensuite une r\u00eagle pour la r\u00e9\u00e9criture URL. &#8230; <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/fonction-php-pour-creer-un-slug-un-identifiant-url-friendly\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;<\/span><\/a>","content:encoded":"<p>Je parlais il n&#8217;y a pas longtemps des slugs dans WordPress et comment <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/wordpress-obtenir-le-slug-dun-post-get_the_slug\">coder une fonction get_the_slug()<\/a>. Il s&#8217;agit d&#8217;un identifiant URL-firiendly. L&#8217;id\u00e9e est de le passer en argument dans l&#8217;adresse et d&#8217;\u00e9crire ensuite une r\u00eagle pour la r\u00e9\u00e9criture URL.<\/p>\n<p>Je vous propose donc une fonction <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/category\/php\" title=\"Voir tous les articles sur PHP\">PHP<\/a> qui cr\u00e9e facilement un slug \u00e0 partir d&#8217;une chaine de caract\u00e8res.<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"wp_syntax\"><div class=\"code\"><pre class=\"php\" style=\"font-family:monospace;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-weight:bold;\">function<\/span> generate_slug<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$str<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#123;<\/span>\n\t<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$maxlen<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> <span style=\"color:#cc66cc;\">42<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>  <span style=\"color:#666666;font-style:italic;\">\/\/Modifier la taille max du slug ici<\/span>\n\t<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$slug<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> <span style=\"color:#990000;\">strtolower<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$str<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n\t<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$slug<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> <span style=\"color:#990000;\">preg_replace<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&quot;\/[^a-z0-9&#92;s-]\/&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">,<\/span> <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&quot;&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">,<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$slug<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n\t<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$slug<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> <span style=\"color:#990000;\">trim<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#990000;\">preg_replace<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&quot;\/[&#92;s-]+\/&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">,<\/span> <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&quot; &quot;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">,<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$slug<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n\t<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$slug<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> <span style=\"color:#990000;\">preg_replace<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&quot;\/&#92;s\/&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">,<\/span> <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&quot;-&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">,<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$slug<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n\t<span style=\"color:#b1b100;\">return<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$slug<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#125;<\/span><\/pre><\/div><\/div>\n\n<p>Voici quelques exemples:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>CecI EST un %^%$&amp; &amp;%&amp; TITRE COMplexe^$)^*)&amp;<\/li>\n<ol>\n<li>ceci-est-un-titre-complexe<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<li>brochure-tarifs-offres-mobile.pdf<\/li>\n<ol>\n<li>brochure-tarifs-offres-mobilepdf<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<li>&lt;title&gt;Untitled Document&lt;\/title&gt;<\/li>\n<ol>\n<li>titleuntitled-documenttitle<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/ol>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>","wfw:commentRss":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/fonction-php-pour-creer-un-slug-un-identifiant-url-friendly\/feed","slash:comments":"0","y:published":{"hour":"16","timezone":"UTC","second":"59","month":"7","month_name":"July","minute":"0","utime":"1312128059","day":"31","day_ordinal_suffix":"st","day_of_week":"0","day_name":"Sunday","year":"2011"},"y:id":{"permalink":"false","value":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/?p=20"},"y:title":"Fonction PHP pour cr\u00e9er un \u2018slug\u2019, un identifiant URL-friendly","guid":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/fonction-php-pour-creer-un-slug-un-identifiant-url-friendly"},{"title":"WordPress: obtenir le slug d\u2019un post \u2013 get_the_slug()","link":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/wordpress-obtenir-le-slug-dun-post-get_the_slug","comments":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/wordpress-obtenir-le-slug-dun-post-get_the_slug#comments","pubDate":"Sun, 31 Jul 2011 15:35:07 +0000","dc:creator":"julien","category":["Wordpress","seo","slug","url","wordpress"],"description":"Dans WordPress tous les posts ont un slug unique. Un slug est tout simplement un nom utilisable dans les adresses (url-friendly). Pandant le developpement de votre th\u00e8me, vous aurez peut-\u00eatre besoin d&#8217;une fonction comme the_slug() ou bien get_the_slug(). Voici deux &#8230; <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/wordpress-obtenir-le-slug-dun-post-get_the_slug\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;<\/span><\/a>","content:encoded":"<p>Dans WordPress <em>tous les posts ont un slug<\/em> unique. Un slug est tout simplement un nom utilisable dans les adresses (<em>url-friendly<\/em>).<\/p>\n<p>Pandant le developpement de votre th\u00e8me, vous aurez peut-\u00eatre besoin d&#8217;une fonction comme <em><strong>the_slug()<\/strong><\/em> ou bien <em><strong>get_the_slug()<\/strong><\/em>.<\/p>\n<p>Voici deux mani\u00e8res de coder ces fonctions. D&#8217;abors la traditionnelle avec les tableaux <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/category\/php\" title=\"Voir tous les articles sur PHP\">PHP<\/a>:<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"wp_syntax\"><div class=\"code\"><pre class=\"php\" style=\"font-family:monospace;\"><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$post_data<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> get_post<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$postID<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">,<\/span> ARRAY_A<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$slug<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$post_data<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#91;<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">'post_name'<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#93;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span><\/pre><\/div><\/div>\n\n<p>Et une m\u00e9thode plut\u00f4t efficace propos\u00e9e par <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/www.joshstauffer.com\/get-post-slug-in-wordpress\/\">Josh Staufer<\/a>\u00a0utilisant\u00a0<strong><em>permalink()<\/em><\/strong> et la fonction PHP <em>basename()<\/em>. C&#8217;est personellement celle que j&#8217;utilise.<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"wp_syntax\"><div class=\"code\"><pre class=\"php\" style=\"font-family:monospace;\"><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$slug<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> <span style=\"color:#990000;\">basename<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span>get_permalink<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span><\/pre><\/div><\/div>\n\n<h2>Snippet pour cr\u00e9er the_slug()<\/h2>\n<p>Sur le site snipplr.com vous pouvez trouver une fonction interessante qui permet de cr\u00e9er &#8216;<em><strong>the_slug()<\/strong><\/em>&#8216;. Tout ce dont vous avez besoin c&#8217;est copier le code suivant dans votre <em>functions.php<\/em>.<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"wp_syntax\"><div class=\"code\"><pre class=\"php\" style=\"font-family:monospace;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-weight:bold;\">function<\/span> the_slug<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$postID<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&quot;&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#123;<\/span>\n\t<span style=\"color:#000000;font-weight:bold;\">global<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$post<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n\t<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$postID<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> <span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$postID<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">!=<\/span> <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&quot;&quot;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span> ? <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$postID<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">:<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$post<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">-&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>ID<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n\t<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$post_data<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> get_post<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$postID<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">,<\/span> ARRAY_A<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n\t<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$slug<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$post_data<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#91;<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">'post_name'<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#93;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n<span style=\"color:#b1b100;\">return<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$slug<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#125;<\/span><\/pre><\/div><\/div>\n\n<p>Cette fonction est extr\u00eamement efficace parce qu&#8217;elle permet l&#8217;utilisation de param\u00eatres, mais pas syst\u00e9matiquement.<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Dans votre boucle, affichez le slug du post courant:\u00a0&lt;?php echo the_slug(); ?&gt;<\/li>\n<li>Partout, affichez le slug d&#8217;un post particulier:\u00a0&lt;?php echo the_slug(&#8217;23&#8242;); ?&gt;<\/li>\n<li>Partout, r\u00e9cup\u00e9rez la variable:\u00a0&lt;?php $slug = the_slug(&#8217;23&#8242;); ?&gt;<\/li>\n<\/ol>","wfw:commentRss":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/wordpress-obtenir-le-slug-dun-post-get_the_slug\/feed","slash:comments":"1","y:published":{"hour":"15","timezone":"UTC","second":"7","month":"7","month_name":"July","minute":"35","utime":"1312126507","day":"31","day_ordinal_suffix":"st","day_of_week":"0","day_name":"Sunday","year":"2011"},"y:id":{"permalink":"false","value":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/?p=17"},"y:title":"WordPress: obtenir le slug d\u2019un post \u2013 get_the_slug()","guid":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/wordpress-obtenir-le-slug-dun-post-get_the_slug"},{"title":"WordPress Thematic: One Page Child theme","link":"http:\/\/sigerr.org\/wordpress\/wordpress-thematic-one-page-child-theme","comments":"http:\/\/sigerr.org\/wordpress\/wordpress-thematic-one-page-child-theme#comments","pubDate":"Sat, 30 Jul 2011 17:17:14 +0000","dc:creator":"julien","category":["Wordpress","parent\/child","project","template","thematic","theme","_project"],"description":"There is something I have really appreciated on web for years: one page website. One of the best example:\u00a0http:\/\/lesscss.org\/ Anyway, as I&#8217;m a big fan of Thematic, I thought that I could use Thematic to create easily this kind of website. So I wrote some lines and made a child theme. Also, you can easily [...]\nRelated posts:<ol>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href='http:\/\/sigerr.org\/wordpress\/a-parent-template-page-to-display-child-page-list-and-details' title='A parent template page to display child page list and details'>A parent template page to display child page list and details<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ol>","content:encoded":"<p>There is something I have really appreciated on web for years: one page website. One of the best example:\u00a0<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/lesscss.org\/\">http:\/\/lesscss.org<\/a>\/<\/p>\n<p>Anyway, as I&#8217;m a big fan of Thematic, I thought that I could use Thematic to create easily this kind of website. So I wrote some lines and made a child theme. Also, you can easily use this child theme as a template page with your own child theme.<span id=\"more-150\"><\/span><\/p>\n<h2>Features<\/h2>\n<p>Basically you will display on only one page, let&#8217;s call it &#8216;page 1&#8242;, every child page (subpage). Your page 1 is a wrapper that contains many page with a submenu. Each part is linked as an anchor using the slug. Therefore URLs are pretty friendly.<\/p>\n<p>The menu is defined once and then printed everytime.<\/p>\n<p><del>I still didn&#8217;t add some JS to make the page scroll up and down but I will&#8230; one day<\/del>. Now it&#8217;s done and its based on <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/archive.plugins.jquery.com\/project\/ScrollTo\">Ariel Flesler&#8217;s plugin<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h2>Documentation<\/h2>\n<p>If you want to use it on its own, you can download the files and add them in the themes folder. If you want to add it to your child theme you can follow these steps.<\/p>\n<h3>The template page<\/h3>\n<p>In your folder create a new php file called &#8216;onepage.php&#8217; and paste this code. The file name is important for the css rules (cf: thematic_body_class function).<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"wp_syntax\"><div class=\"code\"><pre class=\"php\" style=\"font-family:monospace;\"><span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>?php\n<span style=\"color:#009933;font-style:italic;\">\/**\n*\n* Template Name: One Unique Page\n*\n**\/<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n\t<span style=\"color:#666666;font-style:italic;\">\/\/ calling the header.php<\/span>\n\tget_header<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n\t<span style=\"color:#666666;font-style:italic;\">\/\/ action hook for placing content above #container<\/span>\n\tthematic_abovecontainer<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n\t<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$id<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> get_the_id<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n\tthmonepage_navigation<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$id<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#666666;font-style:italic;\">\/\/Define the menu<\/span>\n\tquery_posts<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&quot;post_type=page&amp;amp;post_parent=<span style=\"color:#006699;font-weight:bold;\">$id<\/span>&amp;amp;orderby=menu_order&amp;amp;order=ASC&quot;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n\t<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$count<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> <span style=\"color:#cc66cc;\">1<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n\t<span style=\"color:#b1b100;\">if<\/span> <span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span> have_posts<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">:<\/span> <span style=\"color:#b1b100;\">while<\/span> <span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span> have_posts<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">:<\/span> the_post<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n\t\t<span style=\"color:#b1b100;\">if<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#990000;\">function_exists<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">'childtheme_override_onepageloop'<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#123;<\/span>\n\t\t\tchildtheme_override_onepageloop<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n\t\t<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#125;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#b1b100;\">else<\/span> <span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#123;<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n\t\t\t<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$the_slug<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> <span style=\"color:#990000;\">basename<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span>get_permalink<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#