&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#125;<\/span>\nadd_action<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">'init'<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">,<\/span> <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">'thmonepage_remove_access'<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span><\/pre><\/div><\/div>\n\n<h2>ChangeLog<\/h2>\n<p><strong>0.2<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added JS to scroll<\/li>\n<li>Corrected the page order (now in the menu order)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Related posts:<\/p><ol>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href='http:\/\/sigerr.org\/wordpress\/a-parent-template-page-to-display-child-page-list-and-details' title='A parent template page to display child page list and details'>A parent template page to display child page list and details<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ol>","wfw:commentRss":"http:\/\/sigerr.org\/wordpress\/wordpress-thematic-one-page-child-theme\/feed","slash:comments":"0","y:published":{"hour":"17","timezone":"UTC","second":"14","month":"7","month_name":"July","minute":"17","utime":"1312046234","day":"30","day_ordinal_suffix":"th","day_of_week":"6","day_name":"Saturday","year":"2011"},"y:id":{"permalink":"false","value":"http:\/\/sigerr.org\/?p=150"},"y:title":"WordPress Thematic: One Page Child theme","guid":"http:\/\/sigerr.org\/wordpress\/wordpress-thematic-one-page-child-theme"},{"title":"A parent template page to display child page list and details","link":"http:\/\/sigerr.org\/wordpress\/a-parent-template-page-to-display-child-page-list-and-details","comments":"http:\/\/sigerr.org\/wordpress\/a-parent-template-page-to-display-child-page-list-and-details#comments","pubDate":"Fri, 01 Apr 2011 12:56:31 +0000","dc:creator":"julien","category":["Wordpress","functions.php","parent\/child","wpdev"],"description":"During this WordPress\u00a0theme\u00a0development (based on thematic), I was looking for how to create a nice parent page. Basically in the navigation menu there is a page &#8220;Projects&#8221; and each project is a subpage. But you have to create the &#8220;Projects&#8221; page content to describe what is this part (you also can redirect to the first [...]\nNo related posts.","content:encoded":"<p>During this WordPress\u00a0theme\u00a0development (based on thematic), I was looking for how to create a nice parent page. Basically in the navigation menu there is a page &#8220;Projects&#8221; and each project is a subpage. But you have to create the &#8220;Projects&#8221; page content to describe what is this part (you also can redirect to the first child page, but I dont like it).<\/p>\n<p>Anyway, this function displays each child page title, link and a description. The description is stored in a custom field &#8220;desc&#8221; in each subpage.<span id=\"more-62\"><\/span><\/p>\n<h2>About<\/h2>\n<p>This function is actually easy but could help you to save some time.<\/p>\n<p>The function is based on <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/codex.wordpress.org\/Function_Reference\/get_pages\">get_pages()<\/a>. To make it works you need to create a page and some child page. In each child page create a custom field with the key &#8220;desc&#8221; and fill the value with a little description.<\/p>\n<h2>Install<\/h2>\n<p>Add this function is your functions.php.<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"wp_syntax\"><div class=\"code\"><pre class=\"php\" style=\"font-family:monospace;\"><span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>?php\n&nbsp;\n<span style=\"color:#666666;font-style:italic;\">\/*\n *   Template Parent Page\n **************************************************\/<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-weight:bold;\">function<\/span> sigerr_display_subpage_list<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$parentID<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span>\n<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#123;<\/span>\n\t<span style=\"color:#666666;font-style:italic;\">\/\/Get all the child page of the current page<\/span>\n\t<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$pages<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> get_pages<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">'child_of='<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">.<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$parentID<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">.<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">'&amp;amp;sort_column=post_date&amp;amp;&amp;amp;sort_order=asc&amp;amp;echo=0'<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n\t?<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n    <span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>div id<span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&quot;childpagelist&quot;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000000;font-weight:bold;\">class<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&quot;&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n\t<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>?php\n\t<span style=\"color:#666666;font-style:italic;\">\/\/Echo the list<\/span>\n\t<span style=\"color:#b1b100;\">foreach<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$pages<\/span> <span style=\"color:#b1b100;\">as<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$page<\/span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span> <span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#123;<\/span>\n\t\t<span style=\"color:#000088;\">$link<\/span> <span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span> get_permalink<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#40;<\/span><span style=\"color:#000088;\">$page<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">-&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>ID<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#41;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n\t\t?<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n        <span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>h2<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n        \t<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>a href<span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&quot;&amp;lt;?php echo <span style=\"color:#006699;font-weight:bold;\">$link<\/span> ?&amp;gt;&quot;<\/span> title<span style=\"color:#339933;\">=<\/span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&quot;See the entire page about &amp;lt;?php echo <span style=\"color:#006699;font-weight:bold;\">$page<\/span>-&amp;gt;post_title; ?&amp;gt;&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>?php <span style=\"color:#b1b100;\">echo<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$page<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">-&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>post_title<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span> ?<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n            <span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;\/<\/span>a<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n        <span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;\/<\/span>h2<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n        <span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>p<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n        \t<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>?php <span style=\"colo