cho <span style=\"color:#006699;font-weight:bold;\">$link<\/span> ?&amp;gt;&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>?php <span style=\"color:#b1b100;\">echo<\/span> <span style=\"color:#000088;\">$link<\/span> ?<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;\/<\/span>a<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;\/<\/span>p<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n        <span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;\/<\/span>p<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n        <span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>?php\n\t<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#125;<\/span>\n\t?<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n    <span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;\/<\/span>div<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n\t<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>?php\n<span style=\"color:#009900;\">&#125;<\/span>\n&nbsp;\n?<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span><\/pre><\/div><\/div>\n\n<p>This function is now available in your theme<\/p>\n<h2>Create a Template Page<\/h2>\n<p>Create a new template for wordpress page. If you dont know how, just copy your page.php file and rename it in &#8216;template-page-parent.php&#8217;.<\/p>\n<p>Then add this at the very top of the file.<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"wp_syntax\"><div class=\"code\"><pre class=\"php\" style=\"font-family:monospace;\"><span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>lt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span>?php\n<span style=\"color:#009933;font-style:italic;\">\/**\n * Template Name: Parent\n *\n * This template display a list of each child page with details.\n * Details are stored in a custon field 'desc' in child pages\n *\n *\/<\/span>\n?<span style=\"color:#339933;\">&amp;<\/span>gt<span style=\"color:#339933;\">;<\/span><\/pre><\/div><\/div>\n\n<p>Then locate the piece of code &#8220;the_content()&#8221;. This function print the content of the post. You should probably print the list just after this function.<\/p>\n<pre>&lt;?php display_subpage_list($post-&gt;ID) ?&gt;<\/pre>\n<p>This function print the list into a div#childpagelist.<\/p>\n<p>If you get any trouble, feel free to leave a comment. <img src='http:\/\/sigerr.org\/wp-includes\/images\/smilies\/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley'\/> <\/p>\n<div class=\"info_box\"> I rewrote this post as a <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/sigerr.org\/projects\/wordpress-custom-template-for-parent-page\">project<\/a>.<\/div>\n<p>No related posts.<\/p>","wfw:commentRss":"http:\/\/sigerr.org\/wordpress\/a-parent-template-page-to-display-child-page-list-and-details\/feed","slash:comments":"0","y:published":{"hour":"12","timezone":"UTC","second":"31","month":"4","month_name":"April","minute":"56","utime":"1301662591","day":"1","day_ordinal_suffix":"st","day_of_week":"5","day_name":"Friday","year":"2011"},"y:id":{"permalink":"false","value":"http:\/\/sigerr.org\/?p=62"},"y:title":"A parent template page to display child page list and details","guid":"http:\/\/sigerr.org\/wordpress\/a-parent-template-page-to-display-child-page-list-and-details"},{"title":"Itin\u00e9raire: un formulaire pour trouver la direction avec Google Map","link":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/itineraire-formulaire-trouver-direction-google-map","comments":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/itineraire-formulaire-trouver-direction-google-map#comments","pubDate":"Mon, 14 Mar 2011 04:23:11 +0000","dc:creator":"julien","category":["Webdev","api","formulaire","gmaps","Google","google maps"],"description":"Fournissez\u00a0un itin\u00e9raire personnalis\u00e9 \u00e0 vos clients. Dans votre page de contact vous affichez surement votre adresse et une carte Google Maps pour trouver le chemin. Avec ce formulaire vous donnez la\u00a0possibilit\u00e9\u00a0de trouver un itin\u00e9raire depuis chez eux jusqu&#8217;\u00e0 chez vous. &#8230; <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/itineraire-formulaire-trouver-direction-google-map\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;<\/span><\/a>","content:encoded":"<p><strong>Fournissez\u00a0un itin\u00e9raire personnalis\u00e9 \u00e0 vos clients.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Dans votre page de contact vous affichez surement votre adresse et une carte Google Maps pour trouver le chemin. Avec ce formulaire vous donnez la\u00a0possibilit\u00e9\u00a0de trouver un itin\u00e9raire depuis chez eux jusqu&#8217;\u00e0 chez vous.<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"wp_syntax\"><div class=\"code\"><pre class=\"html\" style=\"font-family:monospace;\">&nbsp;\n&lt;form action=&quot;http:\/\/maps.google.com\/maps&quot; method=&quot;get&quot;&gt;&lt;label for=&quot;saddr&quot;&gt;Enter your location&lt;\/label&gt;\n&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; name=&quot;saddr&quot; \/&gt; &lt;input type=&quot;hidden&quot; name=&quot;daddr&quot; value=&quot;City University of Hong Kong, Tat Chee Ave, ??, Hong-Kong&quot; \/&gt; &lt;input type=&quot;submit&quot; value=&quot;Get directions&quot; \/&gt;\n&nbsp;\n&lt;\/form&gt;<\/pre><\/div><\/div>\n\n<h3>Param\u00e8tres<\/h3>\n<p><strong>saddr <\/strong>= Le point de d\u00e9part de votre itin\u00e9raire<\/p>\n<p><strong>daddr <\/strong>= Le point d&#8217;arriv\u00e9. Dans notre exemple on code en dur notre adresse (j&#8217;utilise l&#8217;adresse de mon universit\u00e9 pour cet exemple)<\/p>\n<h3>Demo<\/h3>\n<form target=\"_blank\" action=\"http:\/\/maps.google.com\/maps\" method=\"get\"><label for=\"saddr\">Enter your location<\/label>\u00a0 <input type=\"text\" name=\"saddr\"\/> <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"daddr\" value=\"&#x009054;&#x004e4b;&#x008def;, &#x009999;&#x006e2f;, Hong Kong (City University of Hong Kong Department of Computer Science)\"\/> <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Get directions\"\/><\/form>","wfw:commentRss":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/itineraire-formulaire-trouver-direction-google-map\/feed","slash:comments":"0","y:published":{"hour":"4","timezone":"UTC","second":"11","month":"3","month_name":"March","minute":"23","utime":"1300076591","day":"14","day_ordinal_suffix":"th","day_of_week":"1","day_name":"Monday","year":"2011"},"y:id":{"permalink":"false","value":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/?p=13"},"y:title":"Itin\u00e9raire: un formulaire pour trouver la direction avec Google Map","guid":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/itineraire-formulaire-trouver-direction-google-map"},{"title":"Ajouter de nouveau \u00e9l\u00e9ments dans le menu contextuel \u201cNouveau\u201d","link":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/ajouter-de-nouveau-elements-dans-le-menu-contextuel-nouveau","comments":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/ajouter-de-nouveau-elements-dans-le-menu-contextuel-nouveau#comments","pubDate":"Wed, 09 Feb 2011 05:57:08 +0000","dc:creator":"julien","category":["windows","fichier","menu contextuel","productiviter"],"description":"Comment ajouter &#8220;nouveau fichier PHP&#8221; dans le menu contextuel windows? Rassurez-vous la technique est simple m\u00eame s&#8217;il est\u00a0n\u00e9cessaire\u00a0de modifier la base de registre. Le but est de rajouter des \u00e9l\u00e9ments dans le menu contextuel pour arriver \u00e0 resultat similaire \u00e0 &#8230; <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/ajouter-de-nouveau-elements-dans-le-menu-contextuel-nouveau\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;<\/span><\/a>","content:encoded":"<p><strong>Comment ajouter &#8220;nouveau fichier <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/category\/php\" title=\"Voir tous les articles sur PHP\">PHP<\/a>&#8221; dans le menu contextuel windows?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Rassurez-vous la technique est simple m\u00eame s&#8217;il est\u00a0n\u00e9cessaire\u00a0de modifier la base de registre.<\/p>\n<p>Le but est de rajouter des \u00e9l\u00e9ments dans le menu contextuel pour arriver \u00e0 resultat similaire \u00e0 l&#8217;image ci-dessous. M\u00eame si cela n&#8217;a l&#8217;air de rien vous gagnerez un temps fou pour\u00a0cr\u00e9er\u00a0un fichier php ou css.<\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2011\/02\/menu-nouveau-windows.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9\" title=\"menu nouveau windows\" src=\"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2011\/02\/menu-nouveau-windows.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"317\"\/><\/a>Note: remarquez le faire du &#8220;firefox document&#8221; <img src='http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/wp-includes\/images\/smilies\/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley'\/> <span id=\"more-8\"><\/span><\/p>\n<h2>Ajouter un \u00e9l\u00e9ment dans le menu &#8216;nouveau&#8217;<\/h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Ouvrir <em>regedit <\/em>(dans la barre de recherche du menu demarrer, rechercher &#8216;regedit&#8217;)<\/li>\n<li>Ouvrir la classw &#8220;<strong>HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT<\/strong>&#8220;.<\/li>\n<li>Rechercher l&#8217;extension de fichier que vous voulez ajouter<\/li>\n<li>Cliquez-droit et s\u00e9l\u00e9ctionner &#8220;nouveau &gt; Cl\u00e9&#8221;, nommez la &#8216;<strong>ShellNew<\/strong>&#8216;<\/li>\n<li>Sur la parti droite, cliquez-droit et s\u00e9l\u00e9ctionnez &#8220;nouveau &gt; Valeur chaine&#8221;, donnez lui la valeur &#8220;<strong>NullFile<\/strong>&#8220;<\/li>\n<li>Fermer <em>regedit<\/em><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>Vous pouvez maintenant v\u00e9rifier que tout a fonctionnez.<\/p>\n<h2>Supprimer un \u00e9l\u00e9ment dans le menu &#8216;nouveau&#8217;<\/h2>\n<p>De la m\u00eame\u00a0mani\u00e8re, retrouver l&#8217;extension concern\u00e9 et supprimez la clef ShellNew.<\/p>\n<p>Note: Comme il faut \u00e9viter les manipulations de base de registre (surtout la suppression), je vous conseil <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/www.nirsoft.net\/utils\/shell_menu_new.html\">ce logiciel<\/a> qui permet simplement de <em>masquer <\/em>les \u00e9l\u00e9ments.<\/p>","wfw:commentRss":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/ajouter-de-nouveau-elements-dans-le-menu-contextuel-nouveau\/feed","slash:comments":"0","y:published":{"hour":"5","timezone":"UTC","second":"8","month":"2","month_name":"February","minute":"57","utime":"1297231028","day":"9","day_ordinal_suffix":"th","day_of_week":"3","day_name":"Wednesday","year":"2011"},"y:id":{"permalink":"false","value":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/?p=8"},"y:title":"Ajouter de nouveau \u00e9l\u00e9ments dans le menu contextuel \u201cNouveau\u201d","guid":"http:\/\/www.tipstf.com\/ajouter-de-nouveau-elements-dans-le-menu-contextuel-nouveau"}]}}